---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="About Miles Scheetz, a mechanical engineering student focused on manufacturing, prototyping, and demanding technical projects."
>
  <section class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-10 px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr] lg:px-8">
    <div>
      <p class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-teal-200">About</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-5xl">Mechanical Engineer<br />(in training)</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-8 text-zinc-300">
      <p>I'm a Mechanical Engineering student with 1.5 years as an engineering co-op and 4+ years of experience in manufacturing. Skilled in prototyping, design-for-manufacturability, and process optimization, with experience working across both production and engineering environments.</p>
      <p>I’ve led and supported projects focused on improving manufacturing efficiency, developing solutions to complex technical problems, and collaborating with cross-functional teams to build and refine processes.</p>
      <p>I’m passionate about applying engineering principles to real-world and extracurricular projects, like rocket club and my hobby railgun. Outside of engineering, I enjoy reading science fiction (especially the Culture books by Ian M. Banks, and Neal Stephenson’s older stuff), lifting weights, and training MMA.</p>
      <p>My ideal role is demanding and fast-paced; it involves long hours, high stakes, tight deadlines, and an uncompromising standard of excellence. x</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
